metadata.name: Cosmo
metadata.description: An exploration of dynamism in the tranquility of colors.Where the contrast of avant-garde forms that know no boundaries in collision with each other creates a balance with tranquil colors, revealing the aesthetics of the composition and all the elements.This  artwork was created for – and exhibited at – the Ninfa Labs x Futura Drops “Otherwise Overwhelmingly Orange” Show in Milan, Italy. 1/1 digital drawing by Movsum.
